## üé® Design Philosophy (CRITICAL - READ BEFORE ANY UI WORK)

**Authority:** `/.claude/DESIGN-PHILOSOPHY.md` is the supreme authority for ALL design decisions.

### Core Philosophy

> **InTime is not software. It is a living organism.**
> 
> We design for timeless professionalism, not temporary trends. Every visual element must serve a purpose or communicate information.

### The Five Design Truths

1. **Truth Over Trends** - Timeless professionalism, not temporary fads
2. **Data Over Decoration** - Every element serves a purpose or communicates information
3. **Asymmetry Over Symmetry** - Nature is asymmetric, so is InTime (7/5, 8/4 grid splits, not 6/6)
4. **Specificity Over Abstraction** - "48-hour placements" not "fast hiring"
5. **Brand Over Blandness** - Bold opinions, unique POV, not for everyone

